{
  "stem": "12684.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was jolted back because I heard my stepfather cough.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The gas as such stayed in us or in me a long, long time-- years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- we were told anybody who was in the gas chamber couldn't-- had to be very careful when teeth extracted with gas.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't do that, very susceptible to that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they said it will stay many years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember shortly after the war, a tooth had to be extracted in Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the doctor said, very easy to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We take gas.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then like a routine question, you have never, ba, ba, ba-- you have never been in a gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh yes!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This man almost keeled over because he knew I would've-- they would have killed me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think it has anything to do with it anymore today, but at the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then also different other gas poisonings after that, so all of this combination of it, I was susceptible.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-mm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took a little while longer to remember things, like a locomotive which doesn't want to go or can't, doesn't have the speed yet, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the only thing I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no he didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pushed in there, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tried not to and then about maybe six or eight years after the fact, some people were there, and we had company.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somehow it came out, and I felt so bad because I didn't want her to know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just said excuse me, please.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got a little bit of cognac and for her, a glass, and for me, a glass.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I felt so bad that she knew it now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then she said to me I should have told her earlier.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
